        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "How can I make my views in the Drawings area larger to fit the page?"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "In the Drawings area of Solid, drag the Scene onto the paper and  right click  in the middle of the scene and go to Scale."
        },
        {
            "type": "link",
            "data": {
                "text": "right click",
